Lucy...Anne Baxter.

1397
01:27:16,985 --> 01:27:19,364
George...Tim Holt.

1398
01:27:20,864 --> 01:27:23,450
Fanny...Agnes Moorehead.

1399
01:27:24,951 --> 01:27:27,539
Jack...Ray Collins.

1400
01:27:29,331 --> 01:27:32,584
Roger Bronson...Erskine Sanford.

1401
